data.description: Centrally located, move-in ready home is prepared for your personal decor and cosmetic enhancements. Open-concept layout boasts oversized spaces for entertainment and relaxation. Morning coffee and/or unwinding in the evening is made easy on the front porch and second floor balcony. The bench seating built into the bay window overlooking the backyard is a perfect spot to kick your feet up with a book! Additional features include a backyard with a deck for entertainment and a detached garage with ample storage space. Brand new roof installed Summer 2022 on the home and garage!
